443
00:54:12,301 --> 00:54:13,970
没事了…没事了，忒修斯
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}It's alright... It's alright, Theseus.{\r}

444
00:54:15,847 --> 00:54:17,431
我怎么了？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}What happened to me?{\r}

445
00:54:17,682 --> 00:54:19,392
你的手
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Your arm.{\r}

446
00:54:19,642 --> 00:54:21,603
伤口上有毒
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}You were poisoned{\r}

447
00:54:26,566 --> 00:54:28,568
其他人在哪？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Where are the others?{\r}

448
00:54:29,069 --> 00:54:32,656
他们在安葬达里奥
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They're putting Darius body to rest.{\r}

449
00:54:51,008 --> 00:54:53,177
她是对的
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}She was right.{\r}

450
00:54:56,389 --> 00:54:59,016
我多年来所怀疑的
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}For all those years, I doubted it.{\r}

451
00:55:03,104 --> 00:55:05,315
怀疑他们…是否存在
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I doubted…their existence.{\r}

452
00:55:07,067 --> 00:55:09,903
你的母亲不虚此生，忒修斯
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Your mother's death was not in vain, Theseus.{\r}

453
00:55:11,488 --> 00:55:14,241
上天注定你的命运
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}It was fate that brought you back...{\r}

454
00:55:14,950 --> 00:55:17,119
和神弓一起
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}for the Bow.{\r}

455
00:55:20,289 --> 00:55:22,833
拿着它，忒修斯
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}With that in your hands Theseus,{\r}

456
00:55:24,460 --> 00:55:26,629
