457
00:57:03,876 --> 00:57:06,503
你是对的，忒修斯
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}You were right, Theseus.{\r}

458
00:57:06,712 --> 00:57:08,923
我的天赋就是我的诅咒
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}My visions are a curse.{\r}

459
00:57:09,632 --> 00:57:12,262
我想用我自己的眼睛重新审视这个世界
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I want to see the world through my own eyes{\r}

460
00:57:13,386 --> 00:57:15,596
用我的心灵去感知
