461
00:57:16,556 --> 00:57:19,767
用我的身体去感受
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}and to touch with my own flesh.{\r}

462
00:57:35,263 --> 00:57:38,141
祭司，看我昨晚搞到什么东西
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Hey monk!I did some "shopping" last night.{\r}

463
00:57:38,391 --> 00:57:40,351
很犀利，啊？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Good weapon, huh?{\r}

464
00:57:53,740 --> 00:57:55,951
很高兴看到你们都活着
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Good to see you're still alive.{\r}

465
00:57:56,410 --> 00:57:59,788
- 我还担心那毒会要你的命　- 的确就差一点
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- I was worried that cow got the best of you. - He almost did.{\r}

466
00:58:00,785 --> 00:58:02,504
