{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}She saved my life{\r}

467
00:58:04,668 --> 00:58:06,420
好像不止救了你命这么简单
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Looks like she did more than that.{\r}

468
00:58:10,633 --> 00:58:12,718
我说…
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Careful...{\r}

469
00:58:13,010 --> 00:58:14,011
你是得到了神弓
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Just because you have that bow{\r}

470
00:58:14,220 --> 00:58:16,264
