{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}doesn't mean I'm gonna treat you any differently.{\r}

471
00:58:16,848 --> 00:58:18,099
好吧
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Good.{\r}

472
00:58:18,266 --> 00:58:19,976
