{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}We have a war to fight.{\r}

474
00:58:25,315 --> 00:58:27,442
地狱山
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Mount Tartarus{\r}

475
00:58:27,546 --> 00:58:29,981
那些信徒相信泰坦
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The faithful believe the Titans are{\r}

476
00:58:29,981 --> 00:58:32,416
仍被关押在大山深处
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}still buried deep within the mountains.{\r}

477
00:58:37,869 --> 00:58:42,567
巨墙是希腊人抵抗你的唯一屏障
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The Great Wall is the Hellenecs only hope against your army.{\r}

478
00:58:49,423 --> 00:58:50,883
屏障？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Defences?{\r}

479
00:58:51,133 --> 00:58:53,837
其实，这里以前是个水坝
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Originally, there was a dam,{\r}

480
00:58:53,837 --> 00:58:56,542
后来希腊人把它进行了改造
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}but the Hellenecs have since adapted it.{\r}

481
00:58:57,723 --> 00:59:01,609
但他们没料到将要面对的是你的军队
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}No one could have anticipated the enemy you have become.{\r}

482
00:59:02,437 --> 00:59:03,901
有多少？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}How many are there?{\r}

483
00:59:04,147 --> 00:59:07,080
这里有多少人我真不清楚，陛下
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}How many have made it here, Your Majesty. I'm not sure.{\r}

484
00:59:07,317 --> 00:59:10,779
- 有多少？　- 我真不知道，陛下
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- How many? - I'm not sure, Your Majesty.{\r}

485
00:59:13,365 --> 00:59:16,118
- 800人　- 城门呢？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- 800. - And the gate?{\r}

486
00:59:16,368 --> 00:59:20,539
20英尺的大理石，重超过12吨
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}20 feet of marble stone, weighing over 12 tons.{\r}

487
00:59:21,123 --> 00:59:23,333
设计时就考虑到要坚不可摧，陛下
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}It was designed to be impenetrable, your majesty.{\r}

488
00:59:25,711 --> 00:59:27,421
你难道不知不管什么城门
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Have you known of a gate{\r}

489
00:59:27,838 --> 00:59:32,635
其实都非固若金汤，嗯…？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}designed to be anything but?{\r}

490
00:59:42,854 --> 00:59:45,648
去找点乐子
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Go be of service somewhere else.{\r}

491
01:00:02,124 --> 01:00:04,001
他们人在哪里？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Where is he?!{\r}

492
01:00:04,209 --> 01:00:06,253
亥伯龙的军团不是驻扎在这的？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I thought Hyperion was suppose to be camped here.{\r}

493
01:00:06,462 --> 01:00:07,880
我们必须继续赶路
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}We should continue.{\r}

494
01:00:08,130 --> 01:00:10,508
过了桥到地狱山还有2天的路程
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Tartarus is another two days along this ridge.{\r}

495
01:00:12,259 --> 01:00:14,303
这是什么声音？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}What is that sound?{\r}

496
01:00:55,847 --> 01:00:57,140
不！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}No!{\r}

497
01:00:58,224 --> 01:01:00,226
我的姐妹们！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}My sisters!{\r}

498
01:01:01,019 --> 01:01:02,729
她们在里面！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They're in the bull!{\r}

499
01:01:09,110 --> 01:01:10,862
不！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}No!{\r}

500
01:01:17,327 --> 01:01:19,246
我的姐妹们！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}My sisters!{\r}

501
01:01:24,835 --> 01:01:29,215
- 我是先知　- 我是你们要找的
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- I am the Oracle! - I'm also looking for.{\r}

502
01:01:31,884 --> 01:01:36,013
忒修斯，他们还有人在这
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Theseus! They are still here.{\r}

503
01:03:08,088 --> 01:03:10,091
到达地狱山前别停下来
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Do not stop until you reach Tartarus.{\r}

504
01:03:10,299 --> 01:03:12,635
这马会一直狂奔直到断气为止
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The horses will run until their hearts give out.{\r}

505
01:03:12,843 --> 01:03:15,471
亥伯龙就要拿到神弓了，赶紧走！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Hyperion will soon have the Bow.Leave!{\r}

506
01:03:41,957 --> 01:03:44,835
原谅我，父亲！原谅我吧！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Forgive me, father! Forgive me!{\r}

507
01:03:46,743 --> 01:03:49,580
我只是为了凡人犯了点错
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I only broke the law to protect the mortal{\r}

508
01:04:30,581 --> 01:04:33,834
我不会允许任何神来帮助你
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}No God will ever again come to your aid!{\r}

509
01:04:35,210 --> 01:04:37,963
从现在开始你就待这！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}You are on your own!{\r}

510
01:04:39,340 --> 01:04:42,385
你明白我的意思么，凡人？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Do you understand, mortal?{\r}

511
01:04:43,511 --> 01:04:45,346
我对你有信心，忒修斯
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I have faith in you, Theseus.{\r}

512
01:04:46,305 --> 01:04:50,309
证明给我看
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Prove me right!{\r}

513
01:04:50,810 --> 01:04:52,645
领导你的人民
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Led your people.{\r}

514
01:05:52,916 --> 01:05:55,169
我终于得到我小时候祈求的马了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The horse I prayed for when I was a boy.{\r}

515
01:05:55,461 --> 01:05:57,087
这马怎么回事？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}What is wrong with them?{\r}

516
01:05:59,089 --> 01:06:00,633
它们要死了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They're dying.{\r}

517
01:06:22,823 --> 01:06:24,574
驻守圣殿那边的人在哪里？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Where are my men?{\r}

518
01:06:24,783 --> 01:06:26,994
还没有回来
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They have yet to return, sire.{\r}

519
01:06:27,744 --> 01:06:30,539
老鹰有没有带回什么信？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}What does the sign on the bird tell you?{\r}

520
01:06:33,042 --> 01:06:34,960
说
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Speak.{\r}

521
01:06:36,921 --> 01:06:38,631
神灵…
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The gods ...{\r}

522
01:06:40,341 --> 01:06:42,677
从天而降
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They came from above.{\r}

523
01:06:42,927 --> 01:06:46,305
- 神灵？　- 陛下，那些神把我们的人全杀了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- The gods? -They appeared and laid waste to the men, my king.{\r}

524
01:06:49,726 --> 01:06:51,561
神灵
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The gods.{\r}

525
01:06:54,189 --> 01:06:55,940
神灵
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The gods.{\r}

526
01:06:56,441 --> 01:06:59,027
和先知一起的几个奴隶都得到他们的庇护
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They protected the slave who travels with the Oracle.{\r}

527
01:07:02,948 --> 01:07:06,785
神灵和他们并肩作战
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The Gods fight on their behalf, sire.{\r}

528
01:07:10,956 --> 01:07:13,500
如果传出去了，我们会阵脚大乱
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}If the men hear of this,there will be panic{\r}

529
01:07:14,710 --> 01:07:17,922
我知道，我知道
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I know, I know.{\r}

530
01:08:07,014 --> 01:08:09,892
和平年代，黑发人送白发人
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}In peace,sons bury their fathers.{\r}

531
01:08:10,393 --> 01:08:14,147
战争年代，白发人送黑发人
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}In war,fathers bury their sons.{\r}

532
01:08:21,154 --> 01:08:23,865
我们正处于战争中吗，父亲？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Are we at war, father?{\r}

533
01:09:04,491 --> 01:09:06,326
我们有重要信息要向议会报告
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I have important information for the Council.{\r}

534
01:09:06,535 --> 01:09:08,161
忒修斯？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Theseus?{\r}

535
01:09:08,370 --> 01:09:10,164
