{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I hope you've come to join the fight.{\r}

537
01:09:31,144 --> 01:09:33,605
军队在哪里？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Where is the army?{\r}

538
01:09:42,739 --> 01:09:45,117
给我说说那个奴隶
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Tell me about the slave.{\r}

539
01:09:47,494 --> 01:09:49,454
是不是你们村的？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}He's from your village, is he not?{\r}

540
01:09:51,373 --> 01:09:52,541
他回答我！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Answer me!{\r}

541
01:09:52,791 --> 01:09:54,752
是
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Yes.{\r}

542
01:09:55,002 --> 01:09:57,504
他是一个异族
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}He was a peasant.{\r}

543
01:10:00,674 --> 01:10:02,635
我也是
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}As I was myself.{\r}

544
01:10:03,803 --> 01:10:07,430
- 对不起，陛下，我不是想…　- 闭嘴
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- Forgive me, Your Majesty. I meant no... - Quiet.{\r}

545
01:10:08,015 --> 01:10:09,684
什么家庭？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The family?{\r}

546
01:10:10,893 --> 01:10:13,313
他的母亲被奴隶强奸过
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}His mother was raped by some villagers.{\r}

547
01:10:13,730 --> 01:10:15,732
谁都不愿意娶她
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Nobody would marry her.{\r}

548
01:10:17,150 --> 01:10:19,819
所以他是一个私生子
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}He was a bastard.{\r}

549
01:10:23,240 --> 01:10:25,158
他什么名？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}And his name?{\r}

550
01:10:25,909 --> 01:10:27,536
忒修斯
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Theseus.{\r}

551
01:10:28,036 --> 01:10:30,414
好极了，我与他见一面
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Very well. I wil meet him.{\r}

552
01:10:40,466 --> 01:10:43,302
赫里奥说他有重要情况向我们汇报
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Helios tells me that you have information useful to us.{\r}

553
01:10:43,511 --> 01:10:46,547
亥伯龙已经拿到伊庇鲁斯之弓
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Hyperion is in possession of the Epirus Bow.{\r}

554
01:10:47,348 --> 01:10:48,891
伊庇鲁斯之弓
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The Epirus Bow?{\r}

555
01:10:49,100 --> 01:10:50,476
是的，大力神赫拉克勒斯打造的
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}-Yes, the weapon forged by Hercules.{\r}

556
01:10:50,810 --> 01:10:53,606
我小时候听说过同样的故事
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I heard the same stories you did as a child.{\r}

557
01:10:53,642 --> 01:10:58,019
神住在天上，而泰坦埋在岩石里
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Gods in living in the clouds and Titans buried in rocks..{\r}

558
01:10:58,693 --> 01:11:00,612
听我说，我开始也不相信
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Listen! I was a disbeliever just like you are.{\r}

559
01:11:00,862 --> 01:11:02,405
但是，伊庇鲁斯之弓是真的
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}But the Epirus Bow exists.{\r}

560
01:11:02,406 --> 01:11:04,932
我知道有很多希腊人…
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I understand that there are many Hellenecs...{\r}

561
01:11:04,969 --> 01:11:07,638
信仰神话和神灵
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}who put great faith in the myths and the gods{\r}

562
01:11:08,193 --> 01:11:10,488
但我们作为希腊议会不会相信这个
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}but we in the Hellenac Council do not.{\r}

563
01:11:10,946 --> 01:11:13,532
神灵都是象征性的，仅此而已
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They are metaphors son,nothing more.{\r}

564
01:11:13,865 --> 01:11:18,335
我们是法治社会讲求的是谈判和依据
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}We are a society of  laws based on negotiation and reason.{\r}

565
01:11:18,413 --> 01:11:20,509
如果你试图通过和亥伯龙谈判
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}If you try to negotiate with Hyperion,{\r}

566
01:11:20,782 --> 01:11:21,498
你会害死我们大家
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}you will be the death os us all.{\r}

567
01:11:21,707 --> 01:11:24,209
难道你要我们接受
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}If I were to accept your council,{\r}

568
01:11:24,460 --> 01:11:27,379
一个科珀斯海湾来的无名小卒的建议？会有用？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Theseus from Kolpos, what would it be?{\r}

569
01:11:27,588 --> 01:11:30,437
封锁大门，准备战斗
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Seal the gates and prepare for war!{\r}

570
01:11:30,473 --> 01:11:32,051
我们正等着外面的部队返回
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}We have Happolyt battalions returning,{\r}

571
01:11:32,259 --> 01:11:34,178
不会有部队回来了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}No one will return!{\r}

572
01:11:34,387 --> 01:11:36,055
最后只有我们几个了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}We are the last!{\r}

573
01:11:36,702 --> 01:11:39,106
你会理解为什么我不接受
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I'm sure you'll understand if I do not accept the advice{\r}

574
01:11:39,110 --> 01:11:42,337
一个魅惑的通灵者和她的异类情人的建议
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}of an alluring palm reader and her peasant lover.{\r}

575
01:11:43,813 --> 01:11:45,982
长官，赫拉克里恩派使者来了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Sir, a Heraklian envoy approaches.{\r}

576
01:11:49,402 --> 01:11:51,488
看见没有？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}There, you see?{\r}

577
01:11:51,738 --> 01:11:55,117
谁都不愿意卷入战争
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}No ruler wishes for war.{\r}

578
01:11:55,534 --> 01:11:58,078
什么建议都不如坐下来想想怎么谈判
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They only wish to be taken seriously at the bargaining table.{\r}

579
01:11:58,704 --> 01:12:01,165
通知议会成员准备谈判
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Alert the Council and prepare a delegation.{\r}

580
01:12:06,128 --> 01:12:09,173
准备！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Bows!{\r}

581
01:12:10,633 --> 01:12:12,677
停下！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Stop!{\r}

582
01:12:14,679 --> 01:12:18,683
停下，再不停下我们就放箭了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Stop, Remain still,or we will be forced to fire upon you!{\r}

583
01:12:23,521 --> 01:12:25,607
把手举起来
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}extend your arms outward!{\r}

584
01:12:28,902 --> 01:12:31,655
他拿着橄榄枝表示和平
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}He bears the olive branch of peace.{\r}

585
01:12:32,322 --> 01:12:34,199
我们国王想找
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}My king wishes to speak{\r}

586
01:12:34,199 --> 01:12:36,810
一个来自科珀斯海湾的叫忒修斯的谈谈
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}with the one called Theseus from Kolpos.{\r}

587
01:12:41,248 --> 01:12:42,750
忒修斯！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Theseus!{\r}

588
01:12:45,127 --> 01:12:47,713
亥伯龙的使者想和你谈谈
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Hyperion's envoy desires a word with you.{\r}

589
01:12:49,256 --> 01:12:52,843
就像我曾预见的，他会张开双臂欢迎你
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Like the vision.He sends for you with arms open.{\r}

590
01:12:54,762 --> 01:12:56,931
想让你归顺于他
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Seeking an embrace of loyalty{\r}

591
01:12:57,140 --> 01:12:59,016
淮德拉…
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Phaedra...{\r}

592
01:12:59,767 --> 01:13:01,894
万一你是错的呢？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Have you never been wrong?{\r}

593
01:13:14,825 --> 01:13:17,160
跨出大门，我们就保护不了你了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}We can't protect you beyond this gate.{\r}

594
01:13:23,459 --> 01:13:25,419
我是忒修斯！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I am Theseus!{\r}

595
01:13:25,628 --> 01:13:28,422
走过来，我有个消息给你
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Come closer, I have a message for you.{\r}

596
01:13:29,256 --> 01:13:30,925
不要冒这个险
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Do not risk it.{\r}

597
01:13:35,471 --> 01:13:37,849
最多，也就少个奴隶而已
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}At worst, you lose a peasant.{\r}

598
01:13:47,233 --> 01:13:48,526
这里？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Better?{\r}

599
01:13:49,027 --> 01:13:50,820
可以
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Yes.{\r}

600
01:13:51,655 --> 01:13:53,657
为什么蒙着脸？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Why do you cover your face?{\r}

601
01:13:53,907 --> 01:13:56,326
我只是信使
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}All are equal in Hyperion's midst.{\r}

602
01:13:56,576 --> 01:14:00,164
带上个面具，完成任务了事，不想惹麻烦
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I myself am only a vessel for of his demands, nothing more.{\r}

603
01:14:00,873 --> 01:14:02,541
他提我的名字干什么？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}And he ask me by name?{\r}

604
01:14:03,167 --> 01:14:05,794
- 他是知道　- 他怎么知道的？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- Indeed he does. - And how does he know it?{\r}

605
01:14:07,338 --> 01:14:09,131
忒修斯，没什么是国王不知道的
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Theseus, there is little the king does not know.{\r}

606
01:14:09,548 --> 01:14:11,592
他知道你没有父亲
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}He knows that you have no father{\r}

607
01:14:11,842 --> 01:14:14,345
其实他也一样，从小遭人排挤
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}and like him,you were cast aside by your very own people.{\r}

608
01:14:14,845 --> 01:14:16,722
他可了解我的愤怒？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Does he know of my rage?{\r}

609
01:14:17,515 --> 01:14:20,935
他知不知道我会用我的剑放干他的血？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Does he know that I live only to see his blood on the end of my sword?{\r}

610
01:14:21,185 --> 01:14:23,271
他知不知道他亲手杀了我母亲？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Does he know that he butchered my mother?{\r}

611
01:14:31,613 --> 01:14:35,575
现在他看到了你的脸，所以他知道了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Now that, he's seen your face, he knows{\r}

612
01:14:44,918 --> 01:14:46,962
你没那么大本事
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}You wouldn't make it.{\r}

613
01:14:47,379 --> 01:14:49,173
懦夫！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}coward!{\r}

614
01:14:49,423 --> 01:14:51,425
跟我走吧，忒修斯
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Embrace me, Theseus.{\r}

615
01:14:51,842 --> 01:14:54,637
他们不会采纳你的建议的
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}They will never give you a say at their table.{\r}

616
01:14:55,096 --> 01:14:57,431
但我会让你成为我的左膀右臂
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}But you could sit at the head of mine.{\r}

617
01:14:58,307 --> 01:15:00,309
这场战争只是个开头
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Long after this war is over{\r}

618
01:15:00,727 --> 01:15:03,563
将来普天之下都会是我的领土
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}My mark will be left on this world forever.{\r}

619
01:15:06,107 --> 01:15:09,819
我的帝国将永盛不落
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The sun will never set on my blood, Theseus.{\r}

620
01:15:10,320 --> 01:15:12,322
这就是我给你的优厚条件
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}This is what I offer.{\r}

621
01:15:12,531 --> 01:15:14,699
这就是恒久
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}immortality{\r}

622
01:15:14,908 --> 01:15:16,994
丰功伟绩可以
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Deeds are eternal, not the flesh.{\r}

623
01:15:17,202 --> 01:15:19,746
但轮不到你
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}... Not the flesh.{\r}

624
01:15:22,833 --> 01:15:25,044
现在你有神灵保佑
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The Gods may be on your side{\r}

625
01:15:25,294 --> 01:15:28,672
但明天…我就放出泰坦
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}but tomorrow.....I unleash the Titans.{\r}

626
01:15:33,886 --> 01:15:35,555
你们讨论什么？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}What was discussed?{\r}

627
01:15:36,013 --> 01:15:37,807
封锁城门
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Seal the gate.{\r}

628
01:15:38,182 --> 01:15:41,185
- 他什么条件？　- 封锁城门
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- What were his demands? - Seal the gate.{\r}

629
01:15:42,520 --> 01:15:44,355
忒修斯…
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Theseus ...{\r}

630
01:16:10,466 --> 01:16:13,302
- 是亥伯龙吗？　- 我差点要他命
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}- That was him, wasn't it? - I was that close!{\r}

631
01:16:45,711 --> 01:16:48,130
我不知道我能否办到宙斯要求我做的
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I don't know if I can do what Zeus asks me.{\r}

632
01:16:52,093 --> 01:16:54,845
如果你有疑虑，说明真相已经近了，忒修斯
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}By doubting, one comes to truth, Theseus.{\r}

633
01:16:59,225 --> 01:17:01,269
神灵不会看走眼
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}The gods chose well.{\r}

634
01:18:49,340 --> 01:18:52,885
长官，前面有动静了
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Sir! There is movement on the front.{\r}

635
01:18:54,262 --> 01:18:56,055
去看看
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Go and look.{\r}

636
01:19:16,587 --> 01:19:18,172
他拿的什么？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}What is he holding?{\r}

637
01:19:21,634 --> 01:19:23,928
弓
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}A Bow!{\r}

638
01:19:40,070 --> 01:19:42,364
打开门！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Open the gate!{\r}

639
01:19:42,614 --> 01:19:45,659
这一切的背后！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Behind it all!{\r}

640
01:19:45,909 --> 01:19:48,996
回头！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Turn back!{\r}

641
01:20:07,181 --> 01:20:09,600
大家听我说！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Listen to me!{\r}

642
01:20:11,936 --> 01:20:13,813
听
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Listen{\r}

643
01:20:17,077 --> 01:20:19,496
你是谁，凭什么告诉我们应该怎么做呢？
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}Who are you to tell us what to do?{\r}

644
01:20:19,746 --> 01:20:22,291
我的确是个小人物，但我是好人，我叫忒修斯！
{\bord0\shad0\fscx75\fscy75\1c&HFF8000&\b0}I am nobody to tell you what to do! I am Theseus, a good man.{\r}

645
